meanings.text: military: violent assault on a stronghold
to enter by force or illicitly

examples.second: Today, Israeli occupying forces once again violently stormed the compound, attacking and injuring Palestinian worshipers with rubber-coated steel bullets and tear gas canisters and arresting several worshipers.
